---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Brendan Bennett">
  <h1>Brendan Bennett</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">It's not that kind of AI I promise...</p>

  <section>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
      I'm a PhD researcher based at the University of Manchester. I study reinforcement learning of large models. 
      In particular, developing more efficient approaches for RL when datasets and/or models are large, like in the case of large language modelling.
    </p>
    <p>
      When I'm not debugging benchmark scripts, I'm probably dancing salsa or climbing. I also play the violin and piano.
    </p>
    <p>
      Here you'll find a record of both my academic work, and that which I find interesting. It's up to you if you wish to find it interesting also.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
</style>
